NOCpulse configuration by Dave Faraldo, 9/05/2000
Updated with macros 8/02/2002

Contents:

  MACROS            -- Macro definitions

  NOCpulse.ini.src  -- NOCpulse configuration source file

  perl-API          -- Perl interface to NOCpulse configuration.  Contents
                       should be installed in the standard search path
                       (e.g. /usr/lib/perl5/site_perl/5.005/NOCpulse/Config.pm).

  BUILD        
  CUSTOMER/BUILD    
  INTERNAL/BUILD    -- RPM build spec.  Uses make_env-specific_files to
                       generate environment-specific NOCpulse.ini files.
                       BUILD and INTERNAL/BUILD should be identical. They
                       BUILD the ini files for internal use. CUSTOMER/BUILD
                       builds the ini files for customer and satellite use.

  env-specific      -- A tempdir for environment-specific files.  These files
                       are generated and should not be checked in.

  npConfigValue     -- A command-line utility to fetch a particular value


